<HEADLINE>
FT  01 SEP 93 / UK Company News: London Finance net assets increase
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Net asset value per share of London Finance &amp; Investment Group, the
investment finance and management concern, expanded to 31.93p as at June 30,
compared with 19.77p a year earlier and 20p at December 31 1992.
After tax of Pounds 40,000 against Pounds 58,000, available profit amounted
to Pounds 79,000 for the six months to end-June, compared with losses of
Pounds 98,000.
Earnings per share were 0.32p (0.4p losses).
As at August 28 the market value of fixed and current asset listed
investments was Pounds 7.97m.
</TEXT>
